        "\n",
        "## Module Learning Objectives\n",
        "\n",
        "By the end of Module 3, students should be able to:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. explain how embeddings support retrieval over text corpora\n",
        "2. build a simple retrieval layer over SEC chunks\n",
        "3. inspect whether retrieved evidence is actually useful\n",
        "4. prepare retrieval artifacts for later prompting and project work\n",
        "\n",
        "## Tutorial Learning Objectives\n",
        "\n",
        "By the end of this tutorial, you will:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Load a small SEC chunk corpus.\n",
        "2. Embed those chunks.\n",
        "3. Build a FAISS index.\n",
        "4. Retrieve the top passages for analyst-style questions.\n",
        "5. Inspect whether the retrieved evidence is actually useful.\n",
        "\n",
        "## How This Tutorial Connects\n",
        "\n",
        "- `M03_Lab1` extends this into more deliberate retrieval experiments.\n",
        "- `M03_Lab2` and `M03_A` build on the same evidence-first workflow.\n",
        "- `M03_Proj` can reuse the same retrieval design ideas in a larger product context.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Setup"
      ],
      "id": "225b922b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "from pathlib import Path\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import faiss\n",
        "from sentence_transformers import SentenceTransformer"
      ],
      "id": "dd22f326",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Step 1: Load SEC Chunks"
      ],
      "id": "cae57bc4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "chunks_df = pd.read_csv(\"../data/assignment01/chunks.csv\")\n",
        "chunks_df = chunks_df[[\"chunk_id\", \"company\", \"item\", \"chunk_text\"]].dropna().head(300)\n",
        "chunks_df.head()"
      ],
      "id": "3aed4c47",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Step 2: Embed the Corpus"
      ],
      "id": "58a157e8"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "embedder = SentenceTransformer(\"all-MiniLM-L6-v2\")\n",
        "embeddings = embedder.encode(\n",
        "    chunks_df[\"chunk_text\"].tolist(),\n",
        "    batch_size=32,\n",
        "    convert_to_numpy=True,\n",
        "    normalize_embeddings=True\n",
        ").astype(\"float32\")\n",
        "embeddings.shape"
      ],
      "id": "6d5b633e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Step 3: Build the Index"
      ],
      "id": "76b2866c"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "index = faiss.IndexFlatIP(embeddings.shape[1])\n",
        "index.add(embeddings)\n",
        "print(\"Indexed vectors:\", index.ntotal)"
      ],
      "id": "36d1383b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Step 4: Retrieval Function"
      ],
      "id": "91310d1e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "def retrieve(query: str, k: int = 5) -> pd.DataFrame:\n",
        "    q = embedder.encode([query], normalize_embeddings=True).astype(\"float32\")\n",
        "    scores, idxs = index.search(q, k)\n",
        "    rows = chunks_df.iloc[idxs[0]].copy()\n",
        "    rows[\"score\"] = scores[0]\n",
        "    return rows[[\"chunk_id\", \"company\", \"item\", \"score\", \"chunk_text\"]]"
      ],
      "id": "f3b38336",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Step 5: Test Queries"
      ],
      "id": "3ded255b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "queries = [\n",
        "    \"cybersecurity and data privacy risk\",\n",
        "    \"supply chain disruption and vendor dependency\",\n",
        "    \"regulatory uncertainty and litigation exposure\",\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "for q in queries:\n",
        "    print(\"\\\\nQUERY:\", q)\n",
        "    print(retrieve(q, k=3)[[\"chunk_id\", \"company\", \"item\", \"score\"]])"
      ],
      "id": "06e2a491",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
